{"tid":285602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭定康：北京試圖介入港府所有部門　攻擊、干預法治","createTime":"2017-06-16T03:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T19:27:15.000Z","uid":53379,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"151f7a6050cc6f31f830cc7820c92fc4474226bc","tid":285602,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:17:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">彭定康：北京試圖介入港府所有部門　攻擊、干預法治</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n前港督彭定康批評，北京對香港自治的管制不斷收緊，北京在港機構試圖介入政府所有部門，並出現對法官、法治的攻擊及直接干預，質疑中國是否真的明白「法治」的意思。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;There has been a steady tightening grip... on Hong Kong's autonomy...You see that in the extent to which Beijing's offices in Hong Kong try to get involved in every branch, every aspect of government.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n亞洲出版業協會（SOPA）昨晚舉辦「2017年度卓越新聞獎」頒獎禮，邀請彭定康演說，但彭因要入院例行檢查未能現身，大會現場播出彭的 15 分鐘錄影演講。<br />\n<br />\n彭定康舉例指，近年種種跡象顯示北京正收緊對港管治，包括介入香港法院正在正常審理的案件（指人大在高院就宣誓司法覆核案宣判前釋法），在香港街頭將人擄走（指銅鑼灣書店股東李波），以及對教育界、新聞自由的干預。<br />\n<br />\n而香港的立法機關更是有所倒退，未有如港人期望般變得更加民主，與 90 年代中方官員的承諾不符。<br />\n<br />\n他形容，若中方不容許溫和、有知識的人掌控自己的命運，他們變得不再溫和也不出為奇。<br />\n<br />\n彭定康質疑，北京加強干預的原因，是中方官員認為世界已不再關心香港，但國際社會、尤其是英國仍在繼續關注香港問題。<br />\n<br />\n彭定康又形容，香港無疑是一個中國城市，但她具有獨特的公民性，而這正正是香港賴以成功的吸引之處，他希望國家主席習近平在今夏訪港時，亦能夠強調這一點。<br />\n<br />\n彭定康又在演說中形容，在港出任港督的一段時間，是他及家人人生中最快樂，也最有趣的時光；雖然他離開香港已經 20 年，仍經常有人問他是否想念香港，人數之多令他感到驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n他指自己無法就香港的每件事作評論，但因英國對香港仍有道義責任，他仍不時評論香港事務，並期望香港能維持作為亞洲最自由的城市之一的地位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/彭定康-北京試圖介入港府所有部門-攻擊-干預法治/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%BD%AD%E5%AE%9A%E5%BA%B7-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E8%A9%A6%E5%9C%96%E4%BB%8B%E5%85%A5%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80-%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A-%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB%2F&d=e%2BxDHBxlilpaJVkZfg9g4EbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=21cf2084\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%BD%AD%E5%AE%9A%E5%BA%B7-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E8%A9%A6%E5%9C%96%E4%BB%8B%E5%85%A5%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80-%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A-%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB%2F&h=cd2a077a\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/彭定康-北京試圖介入港府所有部門-攻擊-干預法治/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qV3GirGvh9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqV3GirGvh9A&d=e%2BxDHBxlilpaJVkZfg9g4EbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c49d6100\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qV3GirGvh9A</a>"},{"pid":"60f8d379f22844ae2baf1b39501a0d709ee0610f","tid":285602,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53aa4e1814ff157a385f03c4a20357c0f2a85ea0","tid":285602,"uid":16453,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:21:25.000Z","msg":"啊媽係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d0b47887e3bc788b82c2e9082c5c42c507f6cb","tid":285602,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:24:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1374465315968d8bb6b523bdbcb9f3deb993ab19","tid":285602,"uid":53619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:24:27.000Z","msg":"同支那講法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慘過同隻狗講"},{"pid":"365edcf4d7f4caaebc4465a667d821cde257d8cc","tid":285602,"uid":48139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:24:29.000Z","msg":"又話港獨無出口<br />\n又唔叫英國收返香港<br />\n依家咁鳩up有乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d658aff9d1d6de60d0269f1dbc96a37ae814fc12","tid":285602,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:36:07.000Z","msg":"開心大發現"},{"pid":"097734cf054329a72f4083fa9baf3032980eda05","tid":285602,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:42:29.000Z","msg":"彭伯 你想點呢<br />\n你講嘅我全部都明 係唔知點算啫"},{"pid":"4219b2f457b767b4ad9c576bbeb2a5edcee8f65d","tid":285602,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:07:36.000Z","msg":"取消中英聯合聲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"912ef5d3ffb0ae4e0bd33a9841bdad7c31b5c586","tid":285602,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:10:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">彭定康批北京收緊港管治 稱干預「無所不在」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170616/s00002/1497549561292\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170616%2Fs00002%2F1497549561292&d=e%2BxDHBxlilpaJVkZfg9g4EbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=de7e451c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170616%2Fs00002%2F1497549561292&h=c242a7d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170616/s00002/1497549561292</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】亞洲出版業協會（SOPA）頒獎晚宴昨日播放了前港督彭定康的錄像演講，談及香港回歸20周年感想。彭定康在演講中批評北京當局對香港管治明顯收緊，認為中聯辦的干預無所不在。他說，香港並非中國普通一個城市，而港人公民意識亦正是香港成功及有魅力的根基所在，希望國家主席習近平在稍後訪港時能強調這一點。 <br />\n<br />\n前港督彭定康昨在活動上透過錄影越洋發表近15分鐘的致辭，大談對香港回歸20周年的感受。他說，自己雖然不願做有關香港事務的時事評論員，但都會不時發表言論，以確保香港能保持作為自由、成功的世界級城市。<br />\n<br />\n指中聯辦干涉官司 質疑內地官不明法治<br />\n<br />\n彭定康表示，香港回歸20年以來，留意到有一些現象發生，例如早前全國人大委員長張德江的發言中，明顯感覺中央對港高度自治有收緊。他又批評，中聯辦對港府干預無所不在，包括有人攻擊法官，甚至干涉香港正在審理的官司。他諷刺地表示，有時自己亦會好奇，其實內地官員是否明白什麼是法治（rule of law）。<br />\n<br />\n強調英國有責任關心香港<br />\n<br />\n彭定康認為，出現這種情况或是因為中央官員認為，97年主權移交後，其他國家就不再關心香港的情况。他分析，近年中國經濟高速騰飛，或令某些人認為香港的成功不再重要。但他強調，其實英國有責任關心香港發展，強調《中英聯合聲明》是雙方簽署的國際條約，以保證香港人的生活保持不變。他指出，一旦北京沒有信守聯合聲明中的承諾，那麼亦可以合理地懷疑當局會否信守其他與國際社會間的條約。"},{"pid":"462216cb798c460b2b97c04ddb4b67090212f6a2","tid":285602,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:38:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又話港獨無出口<br />\n又唔叫英國收返香港<br />\n依家咁鳩up有乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收你班港染無間道想整死英國呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150edac4e7af899b82a83fd8d3827a616acd100a","tid":285602,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:39:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又話港獨無出口<br />\n又唔叫英國收返香港<br />\n依家咁鳩up有乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收你班港柒無間道想整死英國呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"21e0bbd8f278146bca164b4451492f041b015690","tid":285602,"uid":895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:40:12.000Z","msg":"肥彭到底瞓咗幾多年？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2f9062ec940b8a2f04fd559af1cf7756a000e2","tid":285602,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:40:18.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"414a2520e4cd39fccf45cd24982aa952f11c218e","tid":285602,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:43:28.000Z","msg":"屌無老未死港柒港豬<br />\n自己平時點樣奶共投共整死自地喊苦喊忽<br />\n咁多次機會畀你拎上聯合國嘈又冇人去<br />\n英國出晒口術重想人地黎親手幫你班港柒？<br />\n係我就即刻收聲由得港柒慢慢熟啦"},{"pid":"e2bbe158ac4934a41172fee1022c5c3a65ebeb28","tid":285602,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:49:53.000Z","msg":"中共根本唔駛要法治,只要统治"},{"pid":"e5b11e7e8659b90d40e9b531e1f74798efc6da43","tid":285602,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:53:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82e8ec5ac562cc3f0b0f6b8511a03771daa04054","tid":285602,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:55:29.000Z","msg":"廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae4f4fb6de382ace6c825c95626104e711b9fad","tid":285602,"uid":60297,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:56:34.000Z","msg":"開心大發現<br />\n智慧大湧現 yeah"},{"pid":"1b9574f38bbc0d145af0f2cfc17cde04481eb5f5","tid":285602,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T19:27:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}